<% include headerPartial %>

<div>
    <div class="header align-middle" id="header">
        <div class="overlay" style="
        position: absolute;
        margin: 0 auto;
        min-height: 60vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        background: rgba(244, 244, 244, 0.7);
        z-index: 0;">
        </div>
        <div class="headline text-center" style="
        position: absolute;
        top: 20%;
        vertical-align: middle;
        z-index: 1;
        min-width: 100%;">
            <h1>A Travel Vision Platform</h1>                
            <p>Finding your next long-term travel location</p>
            <a href="/cities"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Enter The Cities</button></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="summary text-center my-5" id="summary">
        <div class="w-50 mx-auto">  
            <h1>"Where should I go?"</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row mx-0">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" style="max-height:220px;" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512250431446-d0b4b57b27ec?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=a44ca66de56c79c3f78639b5e948d17a&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1355&q=80">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" style="max-height:220px;" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512553353614-82a7370096dc?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=643c6ebcaf321c2a939e57ed8c0eb485&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1489&q=80">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" style="max-height:220px;" src="https://images.unsplash.com/36/hGibbjg0Rb2fUIoMtU5l__DSC8099.jpg?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=89cdd0f896a0d49a26d8627cca6b41e3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1418&q=80">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-50 mx-auto">        
            <p>The first question we ask our friends when we want to travel someplace new.
            <br>
                An experience sharing platform for travelers who dare to dream of places off the beaten path.
                For those who wants to wants to become immersed in authentic culture outside of resorts/tours, 
                to visit a new lands and stay for a month or more,
                or to find a new home for the expatriate harboring insatiable curiousity.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row features mx-0 my-5" id="features">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <span class="summary-icons"><i class="fas fa-search fa-10x"></i></span>
            <h3>Find</h3>
            <p class="w-75 mx-auto">The world is filled with millions of microcosms of cultures. Finding that new place to visit is frustrating. Let others inspire you with real pictures and stories.</p>
            <ul class="checkmarks text-left w-50 mx-auto">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find amazing food</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find unbelievable standards of living</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find unparalleled culture</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <span class="summary-icons"><i class="fas fa-globe fa-10x"></i></span>
            <h3>Share</h3>
            <p class="w-75 mx-auto">You're the trailblazer in a fabulous new location and want to share this little piece of paradise with others. Share a photo you took and a story revel about.</p>
            <ul class="checkmarks text-left w-50 mx-auto">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Share amazing photos</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Share marvelous travel stories</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Inspire others to greatness</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <span class="summary-icons"><i class="far fa-comments fa-10x"></i></span>
            <h3>Connect</h3>
            <p class="w-75 mx-auto">A picture may be worth a thousand words but the right question can be worth its weight in gold. Reach out to fellow trailblazers, make new friends and reach your dreams.</p>
            <ul class="checkmarks text-left w-50 mx-auto">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find new friends</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find travel buddies</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find the answers you seek</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="start text-center my-5" id="start">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
            <p style="font-size: x-large;">
                Visit Wanderlustoria,
                sign up to share your adventure,
                and be the first to comment, like, or connect with a new friend!
            </p>
            <a href="#"><button class="btn btn-success">Register</button></a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form mx-0 my-5" id="contact">
        <form class="mx-0">
            <div class="row mx-0">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-md-12 text-right border-right">
                    <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg w-50" placeholder="Your name" name="name">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control form-control-lg w-50" placeholder="Email@service.com" name="email">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea class="form-control form-control-lg  w-50"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-block w-50" value="Send">
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
    
<% include footerPartial %>
